                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270712-114-off620 t18270712-114-crimeloc623"></join>. I employed the prisoner as a <rs id="t18270712-114-deflabel624" type="occupation">char-woman</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270712-114-defend657 t18270712-114-deflabel624"></join> on the 16th of June, and on that day I missed a pair of ear-rings and a brooch, from a drawer in my bed-room, to which she had access - I had had no other person in my house; I believe that it was real necessity that induced her to do it; she has a very bad husband, and I believe wanted bread.</p>
